com.google.cloud.bigtable.data.v2.models

Class BulkMutation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.bigtable.data.v2.models.BulkMutation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class BulkMutation
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a list of mutations for multiple rows. Each mutation contains multiple changes that will be atomically applied to each row. However, ordering between rows is not guaranteed.

    This class is meant for manual batching, while BulkMutationBatcher is meant for automatic batching with flow control.
